os involving sparse signals, low-rank matrices, and compressible\nsignals, with various RIP matrix constructions such as sub-Gaussian random\nmatrices and random partial discrete cosine transform (DCT) matrices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jan 2018 21:52:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Feb 2018 18:21:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 12 Feb 2019 16:05:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-13"}
