 uncertainty ($\\Delta$ANC) through the energy ($\\Delta\nE_0$) and the width ($\\Delta\\Gamma$) uncertainties.We also discuss the $\\Delta$\nmethod differences between bound and resonance states pole conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jan 2018 04:35:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Feb 2018 05:46:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 17 Jun 2018 07:14:32 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 8 Aug 2018 00:53:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-15"}
