iding could be part of the mechanisms\nexplaining the formation of solar eruption and the mass and energy supplement\nto the corona.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jan 2018 08:38:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-28"}
